#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*A friendly chat*"
msgstr "*Ingxoxo yobungane*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Talk to your teen about something that they are interested in! 😃"
msgstr "Khuluma nengane yakho ngokuthile enentshisekelo kukho! 😃"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⚽ An easy way to start talking to your teen is to ask them about something they are interested in. For example, you could talk about sports, books, movies, friends, music, celebrities, or school."
msgstr "⚽ Indlela elula yokuqala ukukhuluma nengane yakho ukuyibuza ngokuthile enentshisekelo kukho. Isibonelo, ungakhuluma ngezemidlalo, izincwadi, amamuvi, abangani, umculo, osaziwayo, noma isikole."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👂 You may not find everything your teen shares to be interesting, but it’s important to show enthusiasm and an eagerness to learn."
msgstr "👂 Ungase ungatholi yonke into ingane yakho eyabelana ngayo ithandeka, kodwa kubalulekile ukukhombisa umdlandla kanye nokulangazelela ukufunda."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Create your own Recipe*"
msgstr "*Dala iresiphi yakho*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Let your teen come up with a new meal idea! "
msgstr "Vumela ingane yakho ukuthi ize nombono omusha wokudla! "

#. type=text
#. Strings like @fields.xxx and @results.yyy should not be translated. 
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🍚 Create a new dish with @fields.child_nickname using ingredients they love!"
msgstr "🍚 Dala isidlo esisha ngegama elithi @fields.child_nickname usebenzisa izithako abazithandayo!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔵 Together, choose two ingredients, and ask your teen to prepare a meal using them. For example: chicken and spinach, tomatoes and rice, maize and pumpkin."
msgstr "🔵 Together, choose two ingredients, and ask your teen to prepare a meal using them. For example: chicken and spinach, tomatoes and rice, maize and pumpkin."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "📝 If you enjoy the meal, make it something your family eats weekly, and ask your teen to write it down for you. Give the meal a name and explain how to make it. "
msgstr "📝 Uma ukujabulele ukudla, kwenze kube into edliwa umndeni wakho masonto onke, bese ucela intsha yakho ukuthi ikubhalele yona. Nikeza ukudla igama bese uchaza ukuthi kwenziwa kanjani. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "✨ If your teen notices that you are learning from their cooking, it will boost their confidence!"
msgstr "✨ Uma ingane yakho iqaphela ukuthi ufunda ekuphekeni kwayo, kuzokhulisa ukuzethemba kwayo!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🍚 Create a new dish with your teen using ingredients they love!"
msgstr "🍚 Dala isidlo esisha nengane yakho usebenzisa izithako abazithandayo!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Reflect on the positive*"
msgstr "*Cabanga ngokuhle*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Spread Positivity! 🌈"
msgstr "Sabalalisa okuhle!🌈"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💡 Together, take a minute to think about all the things you did today. "
msgstr "💡 Ndawonye, thatha iminithi lokucabanga ngazo zonke izinto ozenzile namuhla. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "☀️ Take turns sharing one positive or fun thing that happened. This could be something small, like feeling good because you cleaned the house, or something big, like spending time with family and friends. "
msgstr "☀️ Shintshanani ngokwabelana ngento eyodwa eyakhayo noma ejabulisayo eyenzekile. Lokhu kungaba yinto encane, njengokuzizwa ujabule ngoba uhlanze indlu, noma into enkulu, njengokuchitha isikhathi nomndeni nabangane. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⏰ Try doing this every day - even more on the days it feels like you have not done anything special."
msgstr "⏰ Zama ukwenza lokhu nsuku zonke - nakakhulu ngezinsuku lapho kuzwakala sengathi awenzanga lutho olukhethekile."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*What’s new?*"
msgstr "*Yini entsha?*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Learning is fun! 🎓"
msgstr "Ukufunda kumnandi! 🎓"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "\r"
msgstr "\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "❓ Ask your teen to think of a new, fun skill you could learn together. \r"
msgstr "❓ Cela ingane yakho ukuthi icabange ngekhono elisha, elijabulisayo eningalifunda ndawonye. \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "For example: keeping a ball in the air with your foot, juggling, making soup, moonwalking, whistling, saying the alphabet backwards, learning all the countries in Africa. \r"
msgstr "Isibonelo: ukugcina ibhola emoyeni ngonyawo lwakho, juggling, ukwenza isobho, ukuhamba kwenyanga, ukushaya umlozi, ukusho izinhlamvu emuva, ukufunda wonke amazwe ase-Afrika. \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 Take turns trying out the new skill.  Make sure to praise each other and learn and play together!\r"
msgstr "🔄 Shintshanani ngokuzama ikhono elisha. Qinisekani ukuthi niyadumisana futhi nifunde futhi nidlale ndawonye!\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💛 Approach learning the skill in a kind and fun way, and do not judge your teen or yourself for your ability in the skill."
msgstr "💛 Sondela ukufunda ikhono ngendlela enomusa nejabulisayo, futhi ungahluleli ingane yakho noma wena ngokwakho ngekhono lakho kukhono."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Dance moves*"
msgstr "*Umdanso*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Let's get moving! 👋 Dancing is a great way to exercise, have fun, and bond with your teen at the same time! You both get to express yourselves in a fun, relaxed way.  🎵 "
msgstr "Masiqhubeke! 👋 Ukudansa kuyindlela enhle yokuzivocavoca, ukuzijabulisa, nobudlelwane nengane yakho ngesikhathi esisodwa! Nobabili nithola ukuveza imizwa yenu ngendlela ejabulisayo, ekhululekile. 🎵 "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "This game can be played in pairs or a group with everyone taking turns being the leader:\r"
msgstr "Lo mdlalo ungadlalwa ngababili noma iqembu lapho wonke umuntu eshintshana ngokuba umholi:\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "📱 Let your teen choose a song they like and create a set of dance moves.\r"
msgstr "📱 Vumela ingane yakho ukuthi ikhethe ingoma eyithandayo futhi idale isethi yemidanso.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 First person does a dance move and everyone else copies it.\r"
msgstr "👀 Umuntu wokuqala wenza umnyakazo womdanso bese wonke umuntu ewukopisha.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "☀️ Don’t worry about perfecting the dance moves, it’s all about having fun together!\r"
msgstr "☀️ Ungakhathazeki mayelana nokwenza kahle ukunyakaza komdanso, kumayelana nokuzijabulisa ndawonye!\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💡 If you want to, you can perform your dance for the household!"
msgstr "💡 Uma ufuna, ungadlalela umndeni wakho umdanso!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Dance Activity*"
msgstr "*Umsebenzi womdanso*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Try something new and learn a dance challenge with your teen! ✨ Have fun!\r"
msgstr "Zama okuthile okusha futhi ufunde inselele yokudansa nengane yakho! ✨ Zithokozise!\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⭐ Dancing is a great way to have fun together while being creative and moving your body!\r"
msgstr "⭐ Ukudansa kuyindlela enhle yokuzijabulisa ndawonye ngenkathi nidala futhi ninyakazisa umzimba wakho!\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "📱 If your teen uses the app TikTok, suggest doing a dance challenge together.\r"
msgstr "📱 Uma ingane yakho isebenzisa uhlelo lokusebenza i-TikTok, phakamisa ukwenza inselele yokudansa ndawonye.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "😃 Ask your teen to choose their favourite dance and learn it with them.\r"
msgstr "😃 Cela intsha yakho ukuthi ikhethe umdanso ewuthandayo futhi iwufunde kanye nayo.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎉 It’s okay if you can’t dance well, have fun and try not to take it too seriously! \r"
msgstr "🎉 Kulungile uma ungakwazi ukudansa kahle, jabula futhi uzame ukungakuthathi ngokungathi sína kakhulu! \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💡 You do not have to post the video to learn the dance. You can keep it as a memory between you and your teen."
msgstr "💡 Awudingi ukuthumela ividiyo ukuze ufunde umdanso. Ungayigcina njengesikhumbuzo phakathi kwakho nengane yakho."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Check-in chat*"
msgstr "*Hlola imilayezo*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Actively checking in on one another helps to keep relationships healthy! ⭐\r"
msgstr "Ukuhlolana ngentshiseko kusiza ekugcineni ubudlelwano bunempilo! ⭐\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Ask each other questions: “What made you happy today?” 👂 “What was difficult today?” 👂 “How can I help you?” 👂\r"
msgstr "Buzanani imibuzo: “Yini ekuthokozisile namuhla?” 👂 \"Yini ebinzima namuhla?\" 👂 \"Ngingakusiza kanjani?\" 👂\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "For this to help, your teen needs to feel safe while sharing things with you. Be open to their responses. 💚 Teens tend to be more honest when they trust that what they say will not be used against them later.\r"
msgstr "Ukuze lokhu kusize, ingane yakho idinga ukuzizwa iphephile ngenkathi yabelana nawe ngezinto. Zivulekele izimpendulo zabo. 💚 Izingane zijwayele ukwethembeka kakhulu lapho zithemba ukuthi lokho ekushoyo ngeke kusetshenziselwe ukulwa nayo kamuva.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Go easy on yourself if your teen does not want to share their problems with you. 💙 Often, teens are afraid to share as they are scared they will get in trouble. Getting upset with them won’t help - keep showing you love them and give them time! 🌷"
msgstr "Zikhululekele uma ingane yakho ingafuni ukwabelana nawe ngezinkinga zayo. 💙 Ngokuvamile, ingane iyesaba ukwabelana njengoba yesaba ukuthi izongena enkingeni. Ukucasuka ngabo ngeke kusize - qhubeka ubabonisa ukuthi uyabathanda futhi ubanike isikhathi! 🌷"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Express Yourself*"
msgstr "*Zibonakalise*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Dancing makes people happy!\r"
msgstr "Ukudansa kwenza abantu bajabule!\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🌈 This game can be played in pairs or as a group - stand facing each other or in a circle.\r"
msgstr "🌈 Lo mdlalo ungadlalwa ngababili noma njengeqembu - yimani nibhekane noma nibe yindilinga.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎵 Together, choose a fun and upbeat song to play and a person to start the game by creating one dance move.\r"
msgstr "🎵 Ndawonye, khetha ingoma ejabulisayo neshayayo ozoyidlala nomuntu ozoqala umdlalo ngokudala umnyakazo owodwa womdanso.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 The person to their right must copy that dance move and add their own move to it.\r"
msgstr "👀 Umuntu ongakwesokudla kufanele akopishe lowo mnyakazo womdanso futhi engeze umnyakazo wakhe kuwo.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "✨ Go around the circle, each person adding their own dance move to the full song.\r"
msgstr "✨ Zungeza umbuthano, umuntu ngamunye engeza umdanso wakhe engomeni egcwele.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 The first one who forgets someone's dance moves or does it in the wrong order chooses the next song and starts the game again.\r"
msgstr "🔄 Umuntu wokuqala okhohlwe umdanso womunye uyanyakaza noma akwenze ngendlela engafanele akhethe ingoma elandelayo bese eqala umdlalo futhi.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎉 Try new dance moves with this game and have fun!"
msgstr "🎉 Zama ukunyakaza komdanso omusha ngalo mdlalo futhi ujabule!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*2 Truths, 1 Lie*"
msgstr "*Amaqiniso amabili, amanga awodwa*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "This is a fun, quick game, and the point of it is to learn things about each other. Make your answers as interesting as possible! 🎨"
msgstr "Lona umdlalo ojabulisayo, osheshayo, futhi inhloso yawo wukufunda izinto ngomunye nomunye. Yenza izimpendulo zakho zibe mnandi ngangokunokwenzeka! 🎨"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💡 Ask your teen to think of 3 facts about themselves. 2 must be true, 1 must be a lie. \r"
msgstr "💡 Cela ingane yakho ukuthi icabange ngamaqiniso angu-3 mayelana nayo. 2 kumele kube yiqiniso, 1 kumele kube amanga. \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔷 Here are some examples: I hate bananas, I have travelled to Kenya, my favourite subject in school was maths.\r"
msgstr "🔷 Nazi izibonelo: Ngiyawuzonda ubhanana, ngike ngavakashela eKenya, isifundo engangisithanda kakhulu esikoleni kwakuyizibalo.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 Share the facts with your teen and ask them to guess which one is a lie. \r"
msgstr "👀 Yabelana ngamaqiniso nengane yakho bese uyicela ukuthi iqagele ukuthi iyiphi engamanga. \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 Now ask them to do the same, and guess theirs.\r"
msgstr "🔄 Manje bacele ukuba benze okufanayo, futhi baqagele ezabo.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Did you learn anything new about your teen, or did they learn anything new about you? 💛"
msgstr "Ingabe kukhona okusha okufundile mayelana nengane yakho, noma kukhona okusha akufundile ngawe? 💛"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Yes, No or Maybe *"
msgstr "*Yebo, Cha noma Mhlawumbe *"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Are you tired of hearing your teen say yes, no, or maybe to all of your questions? Turn your chat into a game, and don’t allow one-word answers. 🎈"
msgstr "Ingabe ukhathele ukuzwa ingane yakho ithi yebo, cha, noma mhlawumbe kuyo yonke imibuzo yakho? Shintsha ingxoxo yakho ibe umdlalo, futhi ungavumeli izimpendulo zegama elilodwa. 🎈"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔴 Teens are known to give one-word answers to avoid talking. \r"
msgstr "🔴 Ingane iyaziwa ngokunikeza izimpendulo zegama elilodwa ukuze igweme ukukhuluma. \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💡 When you would like to really know how your teen is doing, you can turn your chat into a game. \r"
msgstr "💡 Uma ungathanda ukwazi ngempela ukuthi ingane yakho iqhuba kanjani, ungenza ingxoxo yakho ibe umdlalo. \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⭐ Take turns asking each other questions. The only rule is that you cannot use one-word responses, such as Yes, No, Maybe, Fine, and Okay.\r"
msgstr "⭐ Shintshanani ngokubuzana imibuzo. Umthetho kuphela ukuthi awukwazi ukusebenzisa izimpendulo zegama elilodwa, njengokuthi Yebo, Cha, Mhlawumbe, futhi Kulungile.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⚽ You can ask about things your teen likes or what they did today. For example, how was your day? What are you excited for? Is there anything worrying you?\r"
msgstr "⚽ Ungabuza ngezinto ezithandwa yingane yakho noma ezenzile namuhla. Ngokwesibonelo, belunjani usuku lwakho? Ujatshuliswa yini? Ingabe kukhona okukukhathazayo?\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 It is important to let your teen ask a question as well. Trust is built when your teen can see that you are also sharing your life with them, and not only trying to learn about their life."
msgstr "🔄 Kubalulekile ukuvumela nengane yakho ukuthi nayo ibuze umbuzo. Ukwethembana kwakheka lapho intsha yakho ibona ukuthi nawe wabelana nayo ngempilo yakho, futhi ayigcini ngokuzama ukufunda ngempilo yayo."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Movie World*"
msgstr "*Umhlaba Wefilimu*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Leaving the busy and stressful world behind can be good for our health. 🌱 Take a moment to escape with your teen by creating a superhero story together!\r"
msgstr "Ukushiya izwe elimatasa nelicindezelayo ngemuva kungaba kuhle empilweni yethu. 🌱 Thatha isikhashana ukuze ubaleke nengane yakho ngokudala indaba yobuqhawe ndawonye!\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎈 Ask your teen to imagine that they are a superhero and what their superpowers would be. Flying? Time travel? Mind reading? Super Strength?\r"
msgstr "🎈 Cela ingane yakho ukuthi icabange ukuthi iyiqhawe nokuthi angaba yini amandla ayo amakhulu. Ukundiza? Uhambo lwesikhathi? Ukufunda ingqondo? Amandla Aphezulu?\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "✨ Ask them how they would use these superpowers, and why. \r"
msgstr "✨ Ibuze ukuthi ingayisebenzisa kanjani le mibuso emikhulu, futhi ngani. \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🌈 Help them give their superhero a name, an outfit, and a sidekick, and act it out. If your teen does not want to act, that is fine - talking about it is just as good! \r"
msgstr "🌈 Isize Inikeze iqhawe layo elinamandla igama, ingubo, kanye ne-sayidi khikhi, futhi ilingise. Uma ingane yakho ingafuni ukwenza okuthile, kulungile - ukukhuluma ngakho kuhle nje! \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👑 Now, let them make up a superhero for you. Play the part! You can ask questions, like who the villain would be, or how you became a superhero. \r"
msgstr "👑 Manje, ivumele ikwakhele iqhawe elinamandla. Dlala ingxenye! Ungabuza imibuzo, njengokuthi kungaba ngubani isigebengu, noma ukuthi ube kanjani iqhawe elinamandla. \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💡 Create a story - what happens to the characters? Is it an action story? Is it a thriller, space, sport, adventure, or romance?\r"
msgstr "💡 Dala indaba - kwenzekani kubalingiswa? Ingabe indaba yesenzo? Ingabe into ethokozisayo, indawo, ezemidlalo, uhambo, noma ezothando?\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "➡️ Next time you play this game, you could create a new story or superhero with your teen or continue the story you started together."
msgstr "➡️ Ngokuzayo uma udlala lo mdlalo, ungadala indaba entsha noma iqhawe elinamandla nentsha yakho noma niqhubeke nendaba eniyiqale ndawonye."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Get Active*"
msgstr "*Yiba matasa*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Exercise is a great way to spend time together and it is so good for your health. 🌱 Find a sport or exercise that both you and your teen want to do and try it out together! \r"
msgstr "Ukuzivocavoca kuyindlela enhle yokuchitha isikhathi ndawonye futhi kuyilungele impilo yakho. 🌱 Thola umdlalo noma ukujima enifuna ukuwenza nobabili wena nengane yakho bese niwuzama ndawonye! \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⏰ Even walking for 10 minutes a day is good for you. \r"
msgstr "⏰ Ngisho nokuhamba imizuzu engu-10 ngosuku kuhle kuwe. \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⚽ Together you can walk, run, play soccer, swim, dance, or do any other sport..\r"
msgstr "⚽ Ndawonye ningakwazi ukuhamba, ukugijima, ukudlala ibhola, ukubhukuda, ukudansa, noma ukwenza noma yimuphi omunye umdlalo..\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🏆 Together, think of ways to make it even more fun. Can you jog to a certain point? Take turns being the coach? Can there be a small, free reward, like getting to decide the next activity?\r"
msgstr "🏆 Ndawonye, cabangani ngezindlela zokwenza kube mnandi nakakhulu. Ungakwazi ukugijima uze ufike endaweni ethile? Nishintshane ngokuba umqeqeshi? Ingabe ungaba khona umvuzo omncane, wamahhala, njengokunquma umsebenzi olandelayo?\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🌈 Exercise becomes easier and more enjoyable the more you do it. \r"
msgstr "🌈 Ukuzivocavoca kuba lula futhi kujabulise ngokwengeziwe lapho ukwenza kakhulu. \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 If you or your teen do not like the first exercise you pick, try a new exercise."
msgstr "🔄 Uma wena noma ingane yakho esanda kweva eshumini nambili ningawuthandi umsebenzi wokuqala owukhethayo, zama umsebenzi omusha."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Make up a story*"
msgstr "*Qamba inganekwane*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Creating stories together is a great way to learn the art of storytelling - and to build your teen’s creativity! 📖\r"
msgstr "Ukudala izindaba ndawonye kuyindlela enhle yokufunda ubuciko bokuxoxa indaba - nokwakha ubuhlakani bentsha yakho! 📖\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔟 With your teen, come up with 10 words to use. They can be any words you want! For example: banana, spaceship, fish, water, painting, wasp nest, cooking, wedding.\r"
msgstr "🔟 Nentsha yakho, qhamuka namagama ayi-10 ongawasebenzisa. Angaba yinoma yimaphi amagama owafunayo! Isibonelo: ubhanana, umkhumbi-mkhathi, inhlanzi, amanzi, ukupenda, isidleke somnyovu, ukupheka, umshado.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎂 Start your story with, “Once upon a time, there was a…” and make sure you use one of the words from the list in your sentence. For example, “Once upon a time, there was a family who worked on a **banana** farm.”\r"
msgstr "🎂 Qala indaba yakho ngokuthi, “Kudala, kwakukhona…” futhi uqiniseke ukuthi usebenzisa elinye lamagama asohlwini emshweni wakho. Ngokwesibonelo, “Esikhathini esithile, kwakunomkhaya owawusebenza epulazini **likabhanana**.”\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "📝 Let your teen make up the next sentence using another word from the list.\r"
msgstr "📝 Vumela ingane yakho ukuthi yakhe umusho olandelayo isebenzisa elinye igama ohlwini.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 Take turns until you have used as many words from the list as you can, or until you have finished your story. \r"
msgstr "🔄Shintshanani uze usebenzise amagama amaningi ohlwini ngokusemandleni akho, noma uze uyiqede indaba yakho. \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔔 Be as creative as possible with your story and do not tell your teen what to say. It does not need to be a real story to be a good story!\r"
msgstr "🔔 Yiba nobuciko ngangokunokwenzeka ngendaba yakho futhi ungayitsheli intsha yakho ukuthi ithini. Akudingi ukuthi kube indaba yangempela ukuze kube indaba emnandi!\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎁 Ask your teen what their favourite part of the story was, and tell them yours!"
msgstr "🎁 Buza ingane yakho ukuthi iyiphi ingxenye eyithanda kakhulu endabeni, bese uyitshela eyakho!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Take A Pause with your teen*"
msgstr "*Thatha Ikhefu nengane yakho*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Take a pause with your teen. This helps them deal with stress in a healthy way!\r"
msgstr "Thatha isikhashana nengane yakho. Lokhu kubasiza ukuthi babhekane nokucindezeleka ngendlela enempilo!\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⏰ You could take a pause before dinner, after school, before school, or before bedtime.\r"
msgstr "⏰ Ungahlaba ikhefu ngaphambi kwesidlo sakusihlwa, ukuphuma kwesikole, ngaphambi kwesikole, noma ngaphambi kokulala.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👂 Sit down together and close your eyes. Listen to your breath as it goes in and out. Notice how you feel. \r"
msgstr "👂 Hlala phansi ndawonye futhi uvale amehlo akho. Lalela umoya wakho njengoba ungena futhi uphuma. Phawula indlela ozizwa ngayo. \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⭐ Take 5 more deep breaths.\r"
msgstr "⭐ Thatha umoya ojulile okungu-5.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 When you are ready, open your eyes again. Do you feel any different? \r"
msgstr "Uma usukulungele phinde uvule amehlo akho. Ingabe ukhona umehluko owuzwayo?\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⏸ Ask your teen what it was like to take a pause. Listen and accept whatever they say about it."
msgstr "⏸ Buza intsha yakho ukuthi bekunjani ukuma kancane. Lalela futhi wamukele noma yini abakushoyo ngakho."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Name That Tune*"
msgstr "*Qamba leloculo*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Listening to music is a great way to lower your stress and have fun with your family. 💚\r"
msgstr "Ukulalela umculo kuyindlela enhle yokwehlisa ingcindezi futhi ujabule nomndeni wakho. 💚\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "📻 Gather your family members and choose one person to play or sing a song.\r"
msgstr "📻 Qoqa amalungu omndeni wakho bese ukhetha umuntu oyedwa ozodlala noma acule ingoma.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "❓ Everyone else must guess the name and artist of the song.\r"
msgstr "❓ Wonke umuntu kufanele aqagele igama neciko lengoma.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎉 The first one to guess it right becomes the next person to sing or play a song. \r"
msgstr "🎉 Owokuqala ukuqagela kahle uba ngumuntu olandelayo ozocula noma adlale ingoma. \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 Keep going around until everyone has been able to play their favourite song and let the rest hear."
msgstr "🔄 Qhubeka ujikeleza kuze kube yilapho wonke umuntu esekwazi ukudlala ingoma yakhe ayintandokazi futhi wenze abanye bezwe."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Pass the ball*"
msgstr "*Dlulisa ibhola*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Games are a great, fun way to spend time with your family! \r"
msgstr "Imidlalo iyindlela enhle, ejabulisayo yokuchitha isikhathi nomndeni wakho! \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "3️⃣ This game is best with at least 3 people.\r"
msgstr "3️⃣ Le geyimu ihamba phambili okungenani nabantu abangu-3.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⚽ Find a ball to play. If you cannot find a ball, choose an item you can safely throw around. For example, a bottle cap or a plastic cup.\r"
msgstr "⚽ Thola ibhola ozolidlala. Uma ungalitholi ibhola, khetha into ongayijikijela ngokuphephile. Isibonelo, ikepisi yebhodlela noma inkomishi yepulasitiki.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "➡️ Start in a circle and pass the ball around. \r"
msgstr "➡️ Qala embuthanweni bese udlulisa ibhola nxazonke. \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👋 Start throwing the ball in new directions (up, down, straight, curved, rolling on the ground) and with different forces (hard, soft, medium). You can bounce the ball, throw it in the air, and catch it a few times before passing it. \r"
msgstr "👋 Qala ukuphonsa ibhola ezindaweni ezintsha (phezulu, phansi, iqonde, igobile, igingqika phansi) nangamandla ahlukene (eliqinile, elithambile, elimaphakathi). Ungakwazi ukubhampisa ibhola, uliphonse emoyeni, futhi ulibambe izikhathi ezimbalwa ngaphambi kokulidlula. \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "✨ When everyone gets good at catching the ball, you can start moving around the room, still passing the ball. \r"
msgstr "✨ Uma wonke umuntu eba kahle ekubambeni ibhola, ungaqala ukuhambahamba ekamelweni, usaliphasa ibhola. \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⭐ Can you throw the ball under the leg? Behind the back? Over your head? Block a pass? Have fun with it!"
msgstr "⭐ Ungakwazi ukuphonsa ibhola ngaphansi komlenze? Ngemuva? Phezu kwekhanda lakho? Vimba iphasi? Zithokozise ngayo!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Make Housework Fun*"
msgstr "*Yenza Umsebenzi Wasendlini Ujabulise*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Turn your chores into games! 🏆 \r"
msgstr "Guqula imisebenzi yakho ibe yimidlalo! 🏆\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "☀️ Making housework fun is a good way to teach your teen to be responsible and to rely on themselves. \r"
msgstr "☀️ Ukwenza umsebenzi wasendlini ube mnandi kuyindlela enhle yokufundisa ingane yakho ukuthi iziphathe kahle futhi ithembele kubo. \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "📝 Together, make a list of all the chores that must be done in your home. \r"
msgstr "📝 Ndawonye, yenzani uhlu lwayo yonke imisebenzi okufanele yenziwe ekhaya lakho. \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💡 Make sure the tasks are fair and things your teen can do. For example, washing up, sweeping, mopping, making the beds, and laundry.\r"
msgstr "💡 Qiniseka ukuthi imisebenzi ilungile kanye nezinto ingane yakho engakwazi ukuzenza. Ngokwesibonelo, ukuwasha, ukushanela, ukumopha, ukwendlula imibhede, nokuwasha izingubo.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 Each week, let a different person in the family choose a chore first.\r"
msgstr "🔄 Isonto ngalinye, vumela umuntu ohlukile emndenini akhethe umsebenzi wasekhaya kuqala.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎵 Play some music or turn on the radio. Music is a great way to make a boring task fun!\r"
msgstr "🎵 Dlala umculo noma uvule umsakazo. Umculo uyindlela enhle yokwenza umsebenzi oyisicefe ube mnandi!\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "✅ Tick off the tasks when they are done so you can see your progress as a family. You could offer small rewards as motivation to complete activities.\r"
msgstr "✅ Phawula imisebenzi lapho isiqediwe ukuze nibone intuthuko yenu njengomndeni. Unganikeza imiklomelo emincane njengesisusa sokuqedela imisebenzi.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "📺 For example, you could let your teen watch more TV, spend more time with their friends, choose what they want for dinner, or have something sweet if they do their chores in a fair amount of time.\r"
msgstr "📺 Ngokwesibonelo, ungavumela intsha yakho ukuthi ibukele i-TV eyengeziwe, ichithe isikhathi esiningi nabangane bayo, ikhethe ekufunayo ngesidlo sakusihlwa, noma ibe nento emnandi uma yenza imisebenzi yayo yasekhaya ngesikhathi esifanele.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "❓ If your child does not complete a chore, ask them why, and come up with a fair consequence together."
msgstr "❓ Uma ingane yakho ingawuqedi umsebenzi othile, ibuze ukuthi kungani, bese niqhamuka nomphumela omuhle ndawonye."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*I’m Going on a Picnic and I Will Bring…*"
msgstr "*Ngizoya Epikinikini futhi Ngizofika…*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Memory games are a fun way to strengthen our brains! \r"
msgstr "Imidlalo yenkumbulo iyindlela ejabulisayo yokuqinisa ubuchopho bethu! \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎂 Think of all the things you would have at your dream picnic. \r"
msgstr "🎂 Cabanga ngazo zonke izinto ongaba nazo epikinikini yakho yamaphupho. \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎈 The first person says, “On Saturday, I am going to the park to have a picnic. To this picnic, I will bring...” and they say one thing they will bring to the picnic.\r"
msgstr "🎈 Umuntu wokuqala uthi, “NgoMgqibelo, ngiya epaki ngiyoba nepikiniki. Kule pikiniki, ngizoletha...” futhi basho into eyodwa abazoyiletha epikinikini.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🍅 For example: a sandwich, a ball, a blanket, forks, cups, a dog, or coca cola.\r"
msgstr "🍅 Isibonelo: isemishi, ibhola, ingubo, izimfoloko, izinkomishi, inja, noma i-coca cola.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔔 The second person adds to the first person's list, but must start at the beginning: “On Saturday, I am going to the park to have a picnic. To this picnic, I will bring...” and say the item that the first person said AND then add their own item to the list.\r"
msgstr "🔔 Umuntu wesibili wengeza ohlwini lomuntu wokuqala, kodwa kufanele aqale ekuqaleni: “NgoMgqibelo, ngiya epaki ngiyoba nepikiniki. Kule pikiniki, ngizoletha...” bese usho into eshiwo ngumuntu wokuqala BESE wengeza eyakhe into ohlwini.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 Each time you add an item, you must say all previous items first - in the correct order!\r"
msgstr "🔄 Njalo uma ungeza into, kufanele usho zonke izinto ezidlule kuqala - ngokulandelana okufanele!\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⭐ Each person adds to the list, while remembering all the previous items. \r"
msgstr "⭐ Umuntu ngamunye wengeza ohlwini, kuyilapho ekhumbula zonke izinto zangaphambilini. \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👀 If everyone has a turn, keep going and building your list. The first person to forget an item restarts the game!"
msgstr "👀 Uma wonke umuntu enethuba, qhubeka futhi wakhe uhlu lwakho. Umuntu wokuqala okhohlwa into ethile uqala kabusha umdlalo!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*This is who I am*"
msgstr "*Lokhu ngiyikho*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Self-esteem is the way you value yourself, either in a positive or negative way. Helping your teen to have high self-esteem is a recipe for success! 🏆\r"
msgstr "Ukuzethemba yindlela ozazisa ngayo, kungaba ngendlela eyakhayo noma engeyinhle. Ukusiza intsha yakho ukuba izethembe kuyindlela yokuphumelela! 🏆\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⭐Share with your teen 3 things you like about yourself!\r"
msgstr "⭐Yabelana nengane yakho ngezinto ezingu-3 ozithandayo ngawe!\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "3️⃣ Ask your teen to tell you 3 things they like about themselves. \r"
msgstr "3️⃣ Cela ingane yakho ukuthi ikutshele izinto ezi-3 eziyithandayo ngayo. \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "For example: I am great at treating others kindly. I am great at styling my hair. I am great at football. ⚽\r"
msgstr "Ngokwesibonelo: Nginekhono elihle lokuphatha abanye ngomusa. Ngimuhle ekulungiseni izinwele zami. Ngingumdlali webhola. ⚽\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "If your teen does not feel comfortable sharing these, ask them to write them down. 📝"
msgstr "Uma ingane yakho ingazizwa ikhululekile ukwabelana ngalokhu, yicele ukuthi ikubhale phansi. 📝"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Things I like about others and me*"
msgstr "*Izinto engizithanda ngami nangabanye*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Here is an activity to help you and your teen notice the good parts of themselves.. \r"
msgstr "Nawu umsebenzi wokukusiza wena kanye nengane yakho ukuthi niqaphele izingxenye ezinhle zayo.. \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "☀️Ask your teen to share 3 things they like about a friend or someone they admire, like a celebrity.\r"
msgstr "☀️Cela ingane yakho ukuthi yabelane ngezinto ezingu-3 eziyithandayo ngomngane noma othile ezimthandayo, njengosaziwayo.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "❓ Ask them if they share any of these qualities, too.\r"
msgstr "❓ Babuze ukuthi banazo yini lezi zimfanelo nabo.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💙 You can do the same: share with your teen the qualities you like about yourself or about someone you admire - and what you like about your teen!"
msgstr "💙 Ungenza okufanayo: yabelana nengane yakho ngezimfanelo ozithandayo ngawe noma ngothile omthandayo - nalokho okuthandayo ngengane yakho!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Make a family wish list*"
msgstr "*Yenza uhlu lwezifiso zomndeni*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Wish lists are a great way to set, plan and keep track of your goals and dreams. 🌷 \r"
msgstr "Uhlu lwezifiso luyindlela enhle yokusetha, ukuhlela nokulandelela imigomo namaphupho akho. 🌷 \r\n"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "📝 To start your wish list, gather your family together and grab pens and paper. \r"
msgstr "📝 Ukuze uqale uhlu lwakho lwezifiso, qoqa umndeni wakho ndawonye bese uthatha amapeni nephepha. \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🚲 Allow each family member to write a list of goals and experiences they want to achieve this year.\r"
msgstr "🚲 Vumela ilungu ngalinye lomndeni ukuthi libhale uhlu lwemigomo nolwazi elifuna ukukufeza kulo nyaka.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎂 For example: exercise daily, read 1 book a month, make a new friend, learn to bake a cake, learn to juggle, or go watch the local soccer team play. \r"
msgstr "🎂 Isibonelo: zivocavoca nsuku zonke, funda incwadi engu-1 ngenyanga, yenza umngane omusha, funda ukubhaka ikhekhe, funda ukujuxuza, noma hamba uyobuka iqembu lebhola lendawo elidlalayo. \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔔 Once you have finished, put the list up where everyone can see it daily.\r"
msgstr "🔔 Uma usuqedile, beka uhlu lapho wonke umuntu angalubona nsuku zonke.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎉 As members of the family reach their goals, tick them off the list and celebrate each goal reached. \r"
msgstr "🎉 Njengoba amalungu omndeni efinyelela imigomo yawo, wafake uphawu ohlwini futhi ugubhe umgomo ngamunye ofinyelelwe. \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "❓ As the year goes on, there might be some items some of you have not achieved. Talk to your family about whether you still want to reach this goal or whether the goal has changed. \r"
msgstr "❓ Njengoba unyaka uqhubeka, kungase kube nezinto abanye benu abangakafinyeleli kuzo. Khuluma nomndeni wakho mayelana nokuthi usafuna yini ukufinyelela lo mgomo noma ukuthi umgomo ushintshile. \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔑 If you still want to achieve the goal, discuss with your family what you need to do to tick the goal off your wish list."
msgstr "🔑 Uma usafuna ukufeza umgomo, xoxa nomndeni wakho ngalokho okudingeka ukwenze ukuze uphawule umgomo ohlwini lwakho lwezifiso."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Weekly Goal Setting*"
msgstr "*Isilungiselelo Somgomo Wamasonto onke*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Let’s set some goals ⭐"
msgstr "Asibeke imigomo ethile ⭐"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⏰ It can be helpful to set smaller weekly goals that are easier to reach. This helps us reach our larger goals over time."
msgstr "⏰ Kungaba usizo ukuzibekela imigomo emincane yamasonto onke okulula ukuyifinyelela. Lokhu kusisiza ukuthi sifinyelele imigomo yethu emikhulu ngokuhamba kwesikhathi."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💡Ask your teen for one goal that they would like to achieve this week. "
msgstr "💡Buza ingane yakho umgomo owodwa engathanda ukuwufinyelela kuleli sonto. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔄 Make sure this goal is *specific* and  *achievable* to reach in 1 week."
msgstr "🔄 Qiniseka ukuthi lo mgomo *uqondile* futhi *uyafinyeleleka* ukuze uwufinyelele evikini elilodwa."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💚 You can also share your own weekly goal with your teen and support each other so you can both achieve your goals."
msgstr "💚 Ungakwazi futhi ukwabelana ngomgomo wakho weviki nengane yakho futhi nisekelane ukuze nobabili nifinyelele imigomo yenu."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🎉 Make sure to praise and celebrate your teen for their hard work towards reaching their goal."
msgstr "🎉 Qiniseka ukuthi uyayincoma futhi uyibungaze ingane yakho ngomsebenzi wayo onzima ukuze ifinyelele umgomo wayo."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔔 If your teen does not reach their goal, that is okay. Discuss with your teen the steps they still need to take or how they could reach it a different way."
msgstr "🔔 Uma ingane yakho ingawufinyeleli umgomo wayo, kulungile. Xoxa nengane yakho ngezinyathelo esadinga ukuzithatha noma ukuthi ingafinyelela kanjani kuzo ngendlela ehlukile."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Three cakes and a candle*"
msgstr "*Amakhekhe amathathu nekhandlela*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Working towards big goals can be hard! Here is a way you can help your teen set new goals for the things they want to achieve. 👑\r"
msgstr "Ukusebenzela imigomo emikhulu kungaba nzima! Nansi indlela ongasiza ngayo ingane yakho ukuthi izibekele imigomo emisha yezinto efuna ukuzifinyelela. 👑\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👑 Ask your teen to come up with three things that they are good at, and discuss what they did to become so good at them. For example: keeping their room neat, helping your family with housework, or playing a sport.\r"
msgstr "👑 Cela ingane yakho ukuthi iqhamuke nezinto ezintathu enekhono kuzo, futhi nixoxe ngalokho ekwenzile ukuze ibe yingcweti kuzo. Isibonelo: ukugcina igumbi labo licocekile, ukusiza umndeni wakho ngomsebenzi wasendlini, noma ukudlala umdlalo.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🏆 Next, ask your teen what they wish they were good at. \r"
msgstr "🏆 Okulandelayo, buza ingane yakho ukuthi ifisa sengathi ngabe yenza kahle kukho. \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔑 Remind them that it took work and practice to become good at the skills they have. They will have to do the same for any new goal.\r"
msgstr "🔑 Bakhumbuze ukuthi kudinga umsebenzi nokuzijwayeza ukuze babe nekhono emakhonweni abanawo. Kuzodingeka benze okufanayo kunoma yimuphi umgomo omusha.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⏰ Help your teen break down their goal and set up smaller goals they need to achieve to reach their greater goal. \r"
msgstr "⏰ Siza ingane yakho ukuthi ihlukanise umgomo wayo futhi izibekele imigomo emincane edinga ukuyifinyelela ukuze ifinyelele umgomo wayo omkhulu. \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "📝 It is much easier to achieve a goal if you write it down! This way, you can be reminded of it as you work towards it.\r"
msgstr "📝 Kulula kakhulu ukufeza umgomo uma uwubhala phansi! Ngale ndlela, ungakhunjuzwa ngayo njengoba usebenzela kuyo.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "☀️ For example, if the goal is to be good at football, small weekly goals could be to go to football practice 2 times per week, run at least 1 km 5 times per week, and learn about the sport from other football players in the community or from books or videos they find. \r"
msgstr "☀️ Isibonelo, uma inhloso kuwukuba muhle ebholeni, imigomo emincane yangeviki kungaba ukuya kuzilolongela ibhola izikhathi ezi-2 ngesonto, ukugijima okungenani ikhilomitha elingu-1 izikhathi ezi-5 ngesonto, nokufunda ngezemidlalo kwabanye abadlali bebhola emphakathini noma ezincwadini noma kumavidiyo abawatholayo. \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "✅ It is important to write down these smaller goals and let your teen tick off each task as they do them each week. Seeing themselves reach smaller goals will keep them motivated to achieve the big goal!"
msgstr "✅ Kubalulekile ukubhala phansi le migomo emincane futhi uvumele ingane yakho ukuthi iphawule umsebenzi ngamunye njengoba iwenza isonto ngalinye. Ukuzibona befinyelela imigomo emincane kuzobagcina benogqozi lokufinyelela umgomo omkhulu!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Role Playing*"
msgstr "*Ukudlala indima*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Let’s start acting! ⭐\r"
msgstr "Ake siqale ukwenza! ⭐\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "❓Role playing common stressful social moments with your teen allows them to practise how to respond so they are prepared if this moment does happen. 🌷\r"
msgstr "❓Indima yokudlala izikhathi zokuzijabulisa ezivamile nengane yakho ibavumela ukuthi bazilolonge ukuthi bangaphendula kanjani ukuze balungele uma lesi sikhathi singenzeka. 🌷\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "✨ Ask your teen if they want to role play with you. You can also suggest a topic. For example, asking someone on a date, saying no to drugs/alcohol/sexting, dealing with a bully, getting a bad grade, or dealing with gossip.\r"
msgstr "✨ Buza ingane yakho ukuthi ifuna ukudlala nawe yini. Ungakwazi futhi ukuphakamisa isihloko. Isibonelo, ukubuza othile ngezinsuku ezithile, ukuthi cha ezidakamizweni/utshwala/ukuthumela imiyalezo yocansi, ukubhekana nesixhwanguxhwangu, ukuthola amamaki amabi, noma ukubhekana nenhlebo.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🌙 Your teen could play the role of a friend asking you to drink at a party. You could role play an underage teen who does not want to drink. Encourage your teen to be silly and really get into character with them. \r"
msgstr "🌙 Ingane yakho ingase idlale indima yokuba umngane ocela ukuthi uphuze ephathini. Ungalingisa umuntu osemusha ongafuni ukuphuza. Khuthaza ingane yakho ukuthi ibe isiphukuphuku futhi ingene esimeni sayo ngempela. \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⏯️ After you act out the scene, it is important to talk to your teen about the actions that you role played. You can act out this scenario as many times as you like!"
msgstr "⏯️ Ngemva kokulingisa indawo, kubalulekile ukukhuluma nengane yakho mayelana nezenzo ozililile. Ungalingisa lesi simo izikhathi eziningi ngokuthanda kwakho!"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "*Traffic Lights*"
msgstr "* Izibani Zomgwaqo*"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "A group activity is a great way to bond with others! 💛 \r"
msgstr "Umsebenzi weqembu uyindlela enhle yokuxhumana nabanye! 💛 \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💡 Choose one person to turn and face a wall. This will be the traffic officer. \r"
msgstr "💡 Khetha umuntu oyedwa ozojika abhekane nodonga. Lona kuzoba yiphoyisa lomgwaqo. \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🏁 Everyone else will begin the game at the other side of the room, or if you are outside, at a starting line. Set a long distance between the traffic officer and the players. \r"
msgstr "🏁 Wonke umuntu uzoqala igeyimu ngakolunye uhlangothi lwegumbi, noma uma ungaphandle, emgqeni wokuqala. Setha ibanga elide phakathi kwephoyisa lomgwaqo nabadlali. \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "💚 The game begins when the officer shouts “Green”, and everyone can start moving towards the traffic officer at any speed they choose. \r"
msgstr "💚 Umdlalo uqala lapho iphoyisa limemeza “umbala ohlaza”, futhi wonke umuntu angaqala ukuya ngasephoyisa lomgwaqo nganoma yisiphi isivinini asikhethayo. \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🔴 The officer can shout “Red!” at any time, without looking behind them. When they shout this, everyone must stop and freeze! \r"
msgstr "🔴 Iphoyisa lingamemeza lithi “Bomvu!” nganoma yisiphi isikhathi, ngaphandle kokubheka ngemuva kwabo. Lapho bememeza lokhu, wonke umuntu kufanele ame futhi abe yiqhwa! \r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "⏸ The officer turns around to see if everyone is frozen. If they see anyone moving, they have to send them back to the start line.\r"
msgstr "⏸Iphoyisa liyaphenduka ukuze libone ukuthi wonke umuntu uqandisiwe yini. Uma zibona noma ubani ohambayo, kufanele azibuyisele emugqeni wokuqala.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "🏆 The winner is the first person to get to the officer without being sent back to the start.\r"
msgstr "🏆 Owinile ungumuntu wokuqala ukufika kumphathi ngaphandle kokubuyiselwa ekuqaleni.\r"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👑 The winner then becomes the traffic officer and you can play another round!"
msgstr "👑 Owinile ube eseba iphoyisa lomgwaqo futhi ungadlala omunye umzuliswano!"

